{"tid":341253,"cid":21,"subCid":0,"title":"周杰倫首首歌都有「你說」兩個字？","createTime":"2017-07-30T15:01:02.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-04T08:20:54.000Z","uid":14730,"like":274,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"14e408877248581aeabdfa2db5cd49b269fa9a04","tid":341253,"uid":14730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-30T15:01:02.000Z","msg":"『你說』 苦笑常常陪著妳, 在一起有點勉強 &mdash;《黑色幽默》<br />\n<br />\n『你說』你會哭不是因為在乎&mdash;《最長的電影》<br />\n<br />\n『你說』你也會難過我不相信 &mdash;《安靜》<br />\n<br />\n『你說』為了藝術要砍下一棵樹 &mdash;《梯田》<br />\n<br />\n『你說』這一句很有夏天的感覺 &mdash;《七里香》<br />\n<br />\n『你說』把愛漸漸放下會走更遠 &mdash;《不能說的秘密》<br />\n<br />\n『你說』你想逃開鬆手, 說愛太累、愛的不自由 &mdash;《暗號》<br />\n<br />\n『你說』我像一個小孩, 總愛讓你猜 &mdash;《愛情懸崖》<br />\n<br />\n『你說』給過我縱容, 沉默是因為包容 &mdash;《藉口》<br />\n<br />\n『你說』依賴, 是我們的阻礙 &mdash;《彩虹》<br />\n<br />\n『你說』不該再相見只為了瞬間 &mdash;《白色風車》<br />\n<br />\n『你說』分數怎麼停留誰讓它停留的 &mdash;《鬥牛》<br />\n<br />\n『你說』你好累, 已無法再愛上誰 &mdash;《一路向北》<br />\n<br />\n『你說』你不懂, 為何在這時牽手 &mdash;《給我一首歌的時間》<br />\n<br />\n『你說』淚流著很危險, 如果等雨一起, 不讓同情發現 &mdash;《好久不見》<br />\n<br />\n『你說』你無法釋懷 &mdash;《珊瑚海》<br />\n<br />\nSource: <a href=\"http://bit.ly/2hebD8k\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2hebD8k&d=GWp06nF99vP2HpVgPMUs%2BCwN645TRhVPBLeqKBQ2Igw%3D&h=d17ca087\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/2hebD8k</a>"},{"pid":"bf7c2113200c1846e6e44897a1a5f0dbf38f870c","tid":341253,"uid":1779,"like":10,"dislike":29,"score":-19,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-30T15:03:43.000Z","msg":"咁又點"},{"pid":"0888815c86b617fe7b7358cd13978217343a831c","tid":341253,"uid":20522,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-30T15:06:42.000Z","msg":"飄移已經冇"},{"pid":"db1ba7fbe91cb5a0c56c69c4e05df38dc3fe38f0","tid":341253,"uid":31215,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-30T15:17:00.000Z","msg":"都唔係好多首姐"},{"pid":"b17f045972bce015271013c251535557c44c27ee","tid":341253,"uid":85163,"like":362,"dislike":3,"score":359,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-30T